  <Description><![CDATA[Object for Control Valve]]></Description>
  <RevisionNote><![CDATA[Version 2.0
- ISA-18.2 Alarms]]></RevisionNote>
  <AdditionalHelpText><![CDATA[1. The CVin will be between 0 to 100 and will come from the Output of PCS_PID block
2.The CVOut will be between 4 to 20 and will be provided directly to an Alias tag. Thus the AO card shall be configured for Engineering range 4 to 20
3.Position feedback from the control valve is required. probably Via Hart data only if the field instrument has this capability. if not available use CVIn for this purpose]]></AdditionalHelpText>
